document_data.mainbody:
Lady Alise Cormaeril was a member of the noble Cormaeril family of Cormyr in the mid-to-late 14 century DR.
In the , Lady Alise attended King Azoun Obarskyr IVs birthday feast, hosted by Lord Partic Thistle at Thistleflame Keep. She was accompanied there by Lord Barrit Cormaeril.
